{"tid":2340480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"山東艦高調穿越台海、台灣媒體揭發山東艦冒黑煙原因","createTime":"2020-12-25T13:17:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T18:03:59.000Z","uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"aa6065a0fcb7acae83cf258a9822355d9fc787a8","tid":2340480,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T13:17:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">國防部證實山東艦航經台灣海峽 我六艦八機出海緊盯</span></strong><br />\n2020-12-20 19:07 聯合報 / 記者洪哲政／台北即時報導<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/12/20/realtime/9657275.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=930&amp;nt=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F12%2F20%2Frealtime%2F9657275.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D930%26nt%3D1&h=9291df38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國防部今（20）日證實表示，<span class=\"red\">中共「山東號」航空母艦(CV-17)及所屬護衛兵力4艘，本月17日自遼寧大連港啟航南駛，20日航經臺灣海峽後，續向南航行。</span>這是山東艦於去年12月26日穿越台灣海峽後，第二次穿越台海。上次是由南向北航經台灣海峽北駛，此次則是首度由北向南穿越海峽進入南海。<br />\n<br />\n國防部表示，<span class=\"red\">期間國軍除運用聯合情監偵系統全程掌握、監控外，並派遣海軍各型艦船6艘、空軍各型機8架次，擔任警戒、監控任務</span>，依規定適切應處。<br />\n<br />\n國防部強調，國軍在國人支持下，有信心、有能力守護家園，確保國家安全與維護區域和平穩定。<br />\n<br />\n山東號航空母艦是大陸首艘自製航母於去年12月17日服役、命名，此行至少伴隨三艘護衛艦，計畫前往三亞港。山東號此行引發我軍高度關注，國防部長嚴德發、參謀總長黃曙光今日都在大直衡山指揮所監控此事，我軍艦艇全程尾隨山東艦群。<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Kyou87sv814\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKyou87sv814&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQFcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=7103c2b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Kyou87sv814</a><br />\n山東艦冒黑煙照曝光 邱敏寬揭開背後原因"},{"pid":"dda44dd6434d67932fd79c8218e73ff05ca00196","tid":2340480,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T13:18:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZhBIKNleJYU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZhBIKNleJYU&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQFcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=307ac20a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZhBIKNleJYU</a><br />\n山東艦囂張穿台海、冒濃濃黑煙照曝光"},{"pid":"17f99d0d7e0d6fc41a1954b0d15fd1863a026024","tid":2340480,"uid":191926,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T13:19:24.000Z","msg":"章魚號<br />\n墨魚號<br />\n烏賊號"},{"pid":"9be55a77f6db734038c417a85e129817c4075606","tid":2340480,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T13:25:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/z3-4DQ8a2Hk#t=3m53s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fz3-4DQ8a2Hk%23t%3D3m53s&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQFcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=d303f10a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/z3-4DQ8a2Hk#t=3m53s</a><br />\n軍事專家分析"},{"pid":"cb908416eb1a82935891c0b992b7908c66ab72ca","tid":2340480,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T13:31:50.000Z","msg":"氣場. 你地識條鐵咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d78f4082cd1fd7a0ae5b376e4ec43cdc67318c49","tid":2340480,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T13:39:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.cache.storm.mg/styles/smg-800x533-fp/s3/media/image/2017/07/08/20170708-011726_U1085_M298834_a5bc.png?itok=lgrzrGyb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.cache.storm.mg%2Fstyles%2Fsmg-800x533-fp%2Fs3%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F20170708-011726_U1085_M298834_a5bc.png%3Fitok%3DlgrzrGyb&h=78d4629c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n遼寧艦訪港噴黑煙"},{"pid":"508bcac127853d49ea33a260b1d2011703a69ac7","tid":2340480,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T13:42:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.mobile01.com/attach/202012/mobile01-bea94f493